WorkItem.Description:
Included is an updated version of Excel5 reader supporting horizontal and vertical aligment as well as text wrap at least for the BIFF8 format (covering Excel 97 to 2003). It is based on the latest Excel5 reader from SVN.
 
Needed to merge some functions so I know it may look a bit messy. But please try it out and see what you think. I added the readDataOnly() option so it follows the Excel2007 reader.
 
Try to use the Excel5 reader together with the Excel2007 writer as a (xls-to-xlsx) file converter and inspect the results.
 
Test script:
 
$reader = new PHPExcel_Reader_Excel5();
//$reader->setReadDataOnly(true);
$PHPExcel = $reader->load('biff8-test.xls');
 
$writer = new PHPExcel_Writer_Excel2007($PHPExcel);
$writer->save('biff8-converted.xlsx');
